articles.title: Europe's new Ariane 6 rocket completes key test after many delays - The Indian Express
articles.description: The European Space Agency's Ariane 6 rocket went through a crucial hot-fire test that replicated what the launch vehicle's core stage engine will do during an actual launch.
articles.content: The European-built Ariane 6 rocket completed its important first full-scale rehearsal in preparation for its first test flight, announced the European Space Agency on Thursday. During the test, crews… [+3705 chars]
